name: The 6th Seoul International Conference on Applied Science and Engineering
content: The 6th Seoul International Conference on Applied Science and Engineering (SICASE) is an international platform for scholars, researchers and practitioners to discuss interdisciplinary research and practices in the fields of Biomedical Engineering, Chemical Engineering, Civil Engineering, Computer and Information Sciences, Electrical and Electronic Engineering, Environmental Science, Material Science and Engineering, Mechanical Engineering, Fundamental and Applied Sciences and more. 2019 SICASE will take place from May 21-23, 2019 in Seoul, South Korea. Prospective authors are invited to submit original research abstracts or full papers which were not, are not and have not been submitted/published/under consideration in other conferences and journals. â˜…TOPIC Biological Engineering Chemical Engineering Civil Engineering Computer and Information Sciences Electrical and Electronic Engineering Environmental Science Fundamental and Applied Sciences Material Science and Engineering Mechanical Engineering
